title: Create deterministic child thread sessions
---
Acceptance: profiled rooms can create deterministic child thread session keys from room profile, connector room, and thread/source metadata; child sessions inherit the P11 policy subset only: room CWD, model/template precedence, admin/guest async guard context, and privacy guard. Full tool/codebase/budget/scoped-memory policy waits for P12. Tests cover supported thread connectors. Files: src/session_core.ml, src/session_turn.ml, test/test_room_session.ml, test/test_session_model_override.ml.